Photo: VCGThe fourth session of the 13th National People's Congress (NPC), China's top legislative body, opened its annual session in Beijing on Friday. Xi Jinping and other Chinese leaders attended the opening meeting of the fourth session of the 13th National People's Congress, held at the Great Hall of the People in Beijing on Friday. Premier Li Keqiang delivered a government work report on behalf of the State Council to the legislature for deliberation.